heroImages.title: edit Native stallion marketing platform built-in
heroImages.description: Increase the quantity and quality of your incoming leads by promoting your stallion on Stallion Match. All promoted stallions receive a personalized web link.

heroImages.title: Integrated Stallion Roster Dashboard
heroImages.description: Managing and updating your stallion roster is now simple and can be adjusted at various times of the season to suit your marketing plan. Track the success of your stallions across Stallion Match with critical insights, including search results, race results, and much more.

heroImages.title: Advanced options allow for greater flexibility
heroImages.description: Selling stallion nominations has traditionally relied on inbound calls and emails, often resulting in missed opportunities. Activating this feature online is simple, fast and affordable. Easily customise nomination sales by price, number of nominations and timeframe.

reportsOverview.title: My Shortlist Report
reportsOverview.description: Create your Shortlist of stallions from the Stallion Directory page, then run a detailed report of these stallions over your broodmare. alok

reportsOverview.title: Stallion Match PRO Report
reportsOverview.description: Our most detailed report for broodmare owners who want to find the most suitable stallion - based on customised criteria. Each hypothetical cross will produce a rating, age profile, distance profile and success profile. Both the male and female ancestors are used for a whole of pedigree approach.

reportsOverview.title: Broodmare Affinity Report
reportsOverview.description: 4 key ancestors from the broodmare (sire, grandsire, broodmare sire, broodmare grandsire) are used to find ancestors within the stallion population that will provide positive success trends. A ‘related’ stakes winners list and a psotive sirelines list form part of this report.

reportsOverview.title: Stallion Match Sales Report
reportsOverview.description: A detailed report analyising each horse sold at any sale. Each analysis is given a rating including an Aptitude, Age, Distance and Success Profiles; Impact Analysis, and the top 15 stakes winners comparison table.

reportsOverview.title: Stallion Affinity Report
reportsOverview.description: A great marketing/prediction tool that uses 4 key components of a stallion to identify favourable ancestors within the mare population. A related stakes winners and broodmare sire analysis form part of this report to gain an understanding of mating patterns with your stallion.

reportsOverview.title: Broodmare Sire Report
reportsOverview.description: A Broodmare Sire specific report which is used by breeders to find the most suitable stallion pedigree based on stakes winners globally. The report is tailored by your selection of locations and each stallion is banded/rated by past pedigree success.
